{"tid":1288780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要+緊急］請大家report 呢條立會義士大頭片+report SocREC","createTime":"2019-07-05T18:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T09:15:51.000Z","uid":109368,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a44493cb9626aa067f1f5abe367e2c75389db73e","tid":1288780,"uid":109368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:44:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今次係第一次開post  關乎義士安全 請大家廣傳阿唔該！！！<br />\n事源SocREC post咗一條立會片 有曬義士大頭<br />\n俾藍絲page share曬要用嚟做檢控證據<br />\n發現嘅時候事發已經一兩日 但請大家盡力report呢條片+藍絲page<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HPHxXH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HPHxXH.png&h=9e86c293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外都重要嘅係<br />\nReport SocREC個page！！！！！！<br />\n呢個channel已經唔止一次因爲拍攝示威者而令佢地面對被政治檢控嘅威脅！（EG. 魚蛋）<br />\n無論係有心定無意 都值得被report <br />\n呢個時候真係唔容許有呢種欠缺記者專業知識嘅豬隊友出現 影響大家安危！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"451d9e0e38fd1e09c4333c5927437071fd74e5a0","tid":1288780,"uid":109368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:47:39.000Z","msg":"推阿!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"5eb9de3b4888c2ef17fc85a1c075d9818eba6d76","tid":1288780,"uid":109368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:49:03.000Z","msg":"真係唔知有冇用但大家幫幫手啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3d665c1d156176577f49832875927978e570e5","tid":1288780,"uid":109368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:50:50.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！"},{"pid":"d89127792386fa9e8abff2666de7d7f809f3672a","tid":1288780,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61827026b419a1249205a33f7876105581933531","tid":1288780,"uid":34742,"li